### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/users
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### 1. REGISTER NEW USER
### ========================================

### Register a Buyer (Default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "marycharity5@gmail.com",
  "username": "Mary Charity"
}

### Register a Seller
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "seller@example.com",
  "username": "cool_seller",
  "userType": "seller"
}

### Register with Custom UserType
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "username": "admin_user",
  "userType": "admin"
}

### Register with Missing Fields (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Register with Invalid Email (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "username": "testuser"
}

### Register with Short Username (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "ab"
}

### ========================================
### 2. LOGIN
### ========================================

### Login with Registered User
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "GENERATED_PASSWORD_FROM_EMAIL"
}

### Login with Seller Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "seller@example.com",
  "password": "GENERATED_PASSWORD_FROM_EMAIL"
}

### Login with Wrong Password (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword123"
}

### Login with Non-existent Email (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ========================================
### 3. GET PROFILE (Protected Route)
### ========================================

### Get Profile with Token (Replace with actual token from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### ========================================
### 4. PASSWORD RESET (If implemented)
### ========================================

### Request Password Reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/reset-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}